Package python.symbolTable

This package contains all class used to create a symbol table from an AST.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArgumentSymbol
    Class defining a mandatory argument for a FunctionSymbol.
    FunctionSymbol
    Class defining a function in a symbolTable.
    OptionalArgumentSymbol
    Class defining an optional argument for a FunctionSymbol.
    SymbolTable
    Class defining a symbol table gathering the variables and functions of an AST.
    SymbolTableGenerator
    Factory class used to instantiate or complete a SymbolTable from a AST (or a subtree).
    VariableSymbol
    Class defining a variable of a SymbolTable.

Package python.symbolTable Description

This package contains all class used to create a symbol table from an AST.
